    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in great shape and has been well-cared for, making it a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner. While it shows a few minor signs of normal use, it remains a solid, high-quality ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. You'll love how dependable and clean this car is\u2014it's truly a wonderful value!",
      "price": 34500.0,
